<p class="ayah 37-7" id="7" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَحِفْظًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (to) guard</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">against</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَيْطَـٰنٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">devil</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّارِدٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">rebellious,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>7<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
