<p class="ayah 37-23" id="23" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن دُونِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Besides</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱهْدُوهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then lead them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صِرَٲطِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Path</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْجَحِيمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Hellfire.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>23<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 37-24" id="24" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقِفُوهُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And stop them;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">indeed, they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّسْــُٔولُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) to be questioned.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>24<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
