<p class="ayah 37-39" id="39" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُجْزَوْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will be recompensed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you used (to)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">do,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>39<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 37-40" id="40" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِبَادَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) slaves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُخْلَصِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the chosen ones.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>40<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
