<p class="ayah 37-46" id="46" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْضَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">White,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَذَّةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">delicious</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّلشَّـٰرِبِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the drinkers;</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>46<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
