<p class="ayah 37-48" id="48" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعِندَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And with them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَـٰصِرَٲتُ ٱلطَّرْفِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) companions of modest gaze</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِينٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(having) beautiful eyes,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>48<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 37-49" id="49" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَأَنَّهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">As if they were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْضٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">eggs,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّكْنُونٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">well protected.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>49<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 37-50" id="50" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَقْبَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (will) approach</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْضُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">some of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْضٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">others</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتَسَآءَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">questioning one another.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>50<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
