<p class="ayah 37-178" id="178" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتَوَلَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So turn away</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حِينٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a time.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>178<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 37-179" id="179" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَبْصِرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And see,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَسَوْفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so soon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُبْصِرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they will see.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>179<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 37-180" id="180" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سُبْحَـٰنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Glory</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(be to) your Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعِزَّةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Honor,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">above what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَصِفُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they attribute.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>180<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 37-181" id="181" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَسَلَـٰمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And peace be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُرْسَلِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Messengers.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>181<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
